gov.nih.nlm.meme.common
Class PasswordAuthenticator

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.common.PasswordAuthenticator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Authenticator
public class PasswordAuthenticator
extends Object
implements Authenticator

Implements an authentication hand-shake with PasswordAuthentication to provide username/password access to resources. It extends the Authenticator functionality with the setUsernameAndPassword(String, char[]) method which allows an Authentication object to provide the necessary information for authentication.

Author:
MEME Group
See Also:
PasswordAuthentication, Authentication
